    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>★加入我们★</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《栖云异梦》官方交流群3：772664622</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> B站账号：山灰猫的栖云异梦</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 小红书账号：山灰猫的栖云异梦</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 抖音账号：山灰猫的栖云异梦</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款AVG叙事解谜游戏，故事背景为架空的19世纪末欧洲，玩家将以主角的身份进行体验。游戏分为三条主线和一条隐藏线，玩家将分章节体验每条线的剧情，最终根据属性的数值决定玩家达成不同结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世间流传着这个一个故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当遥远的风从大洋彼岸吹来的时候，神秘的东方带来了华缎、瓷器，和——奇迹。有小部分人奉它为神明，但更多人则惧它如斯。世人高举着镰刀和火把，宛如看到中世纪的巫师般避之不及，如此唾弃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很多年后，人们将它忘记了，奇迹终究变为遥远的传言堙灭于世间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在19世纪末的架空欧洲，玩家将扮演一名在宠物店打工的少年，在一天偶然踏入一家神秘的玩具店，发现了与众不同的诡异事情，从此开始了命运的转动——奇迹？传言？死而复生？玩家在与三位店员的接触中逐渐探索真相，或许……事情并非你看到的那样简单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷雾笼罩下的城市深处，万籁俱寂的黑夜中，有一处灯光指引着误入迷途的行人，爱与悲伤交缠在一起，逐渐揭开一场有关五年前火灾的真相。复活的已逝之人，残缺的记忆，熟悉的外表下掩盖的，究竟是罪恶还是救赎？而他们，到底是湮灭亦或是重生？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随无形的力量，探索玩具店里的故事，真相……或许更加悲伤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本篇为《栖云异梦》系列欧洲番外篇，当来自栖云洲的古玉流入海外，神秘的东方力量将掀起新的篇章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras/cea15a4cc4f21a7545e388cbcd5a00e6.avif?t=1770029758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras_big/cea15a4cc4f21a7545e388cbcd5a00e6.avif?t=1770029758 width=800 height=2164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras/d775e3b6c7df6c627a3bbed2d6185a2e.avif?t=1770029758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras_big/d775e3b6c7df6c627a3bbed2d6185a2e.avif?t=1770029758 width=800 height=1865 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras/ddc08bd91b66d9d5b880ee25fc598ca6.avif?t=1770029758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras_big/ddc08bd91b66d9d5b880ee25fc598ca6.avif?t=1770029758 width=800 height=1155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras/b6e189f8f64f05d8fdd319166052d0d1.avif?t=1770029758\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061100/extras_big/b6e189f8f64f05d8fdd319166052d0d1.avif?t=1770029758 width=800 height=2244 /></span></p>",
